33
00:03:13,350 --> 00:03:17,750
Engagement...

34
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:20,250
He's in a world of his own.

35
00:03:21,950 --> 00:03:27,750
"The Secrets of Pop Stars (Part 1)"

36
00:03:27,750 --> 00:03:31,850
Well, thank you, Yoko.

37
00:03:31,850 --> 00:03:34,950
It is a great pleasure to be invited

38
00:03:34,950 --> 00:03:37,350
to the engagement party of your best friend.

39
00:03:37,350 --> 00:03:38,350
The pleasure is mine.

40
00:03:38,350 --> 00:03:42,550
"Yoko Okino (22), Idol" -I'm sorry for inviting you on such short notice.

41
00:03:42,550 --> 00:03:43,850
You must be surprised.

42
00:03:43,850 --> 00:03:46,150
No. Not at all.

43
00:03:46,150 --> 00:03:47,750
You're, right.

44
00:03:47,750 --> 00:03:50,750
