45
00:03:50,750 --> 00:03:55,250
So? Who is she? Your engaged friend?

46
00:03:55,250 --> 00:03:56,850
You will see her soon.

47
00:03:56,850 --> 00:03:58,850
All of you know her very well.

48
00:03:58,850 --> 00:04:00,050
Do I know the person well?

49
00:04:00,050 --> 00:04:01,250
Hi, Yoko.

50
00:04:02,350 --> 00:04:03,750
Oh, dear...

51
00:04:03,750 --> 00:04:06,150
You really brought him here.

52
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:09,050
The renowned Detective Kogoro Mouri.

53
00:04:10,650 --> 00:04:12,250
If I'm not mistaken, you're...

54
00:04:14,550 --> 00:04:16,950
the person playing the role of Detective Samonji.

55
00:04:16,950 --> 00:04:18,650
Osamu Kenzaki.

56
00:04:18,650 --> 00:04:20,950
"Osamu Kenzaki (26), Actor"

57
00:04:22,550 --> 00:04:26,950
So, then, you're Yoko's engaged friend?

58
00:04:26,950 --> 00:04:29,650
Well, actually, no... I am her future husband-to-be.

59
00:04:29,650 --> 00:04:34,250
Yoko's best friend is my future bride.

60
00:04:34,250 --> 00:04:35,750
Anyway, I think it's really great that you brought

61
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:38,050
the renowned Detective Mouri to us.

62
00:04:38,050 --> 00:04:40,150
