74
00:05:29,450 --> 00:05:31,950
"Kaoru Kusano (20), Actress" -I'm recently being hassled by a stalker.

75
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:34,250
I saw a strange man looking through the peep hole of the door,

76
00:05:34,250 --> 00:05:37,150
