77
00:05:37,150 --> 00:05:40,250
If you are his admirer or fan, you should have known his face?

78
00:05:40,250 --> 00:05:44,050
Well then, Yoko's friend who got engaged to Mr. Kenzaki is...

79
00:05:44,050 --> 00:05:45,450
Yes, it is me.

80
00:05:46,850 --> 00:05:50,050
The formal wedding ceremony will be this coming spring.

81
00:05:50,050 --> 00:05:53,250
It's still off-the-records to the media.

82
00:05:53,250 --> 00:05:54,950
That reminds me,

83
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:59,050
Kaoru co-starred with Mr. Kenzaki in "Detective Samonji".

84
00:05:59,050 --> 00:06:00,950
That's right.

85
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:04,050
We brought them both here to celebrate and tease them,

86
00:06:04,050 --> 00:06:07,250
while watching the TV program being aired tonight.

87
00:06:07,250 --> 00:06:09,950
"Yuki Takeno (22), Multi-talented" -The perfect couple...

88
00:06:11,050 --> 00:06:12,550
Yuki Takeno.

89
00:06:12,550 --> 00:06:15,850
I think your nails are a little bit too flashy, Yuki.

90
00:06:17,150 --> 00:06:20,450
These false nails are cool, isn't it?

91
00:06:20,450 --> 00:06:25,250
But it's a pity, Yoko Okino.

92
00:06:25,250 --> 00:06:28,550
Yuki Takeno and Kaoru Kusano...

93
00:06:28,550 --> 00:06:31,050
One more person, and all four would be present.

94
00:06:31,050 --> 00:06:33,550
How regrettable indeed.

95
00:06:34,550 --> 00:06:36,650
Did someone call me?

96
00:06:38,250 --> 00:06:39,450
Terumi.

97
00:06:40,650 --> 00:06:43,750
Well, well, you have turned out quite nicely.

98
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:48,350
"Terumi Hoshino (23), Actress" -Well, Yoko told me that I had to come.

99
00:06:48,350 --> 00:06:51,050
Am I interrupting? If so, I can leave.

100
00:06:51,050 --> 00:06:52,150
Come, come.

101
00:06:52,150 --> 00:06:55,850
Now the four "Earth Ladies" have gathered here again after a long recess.

102
00:06:55,850 --> 00:06:57,650
Earth Ladies?

103
00:06:57,650 --> 00:07:00,350
You may not know, but...

104
00:07:00,350 --> 00:07:02,550
Kaoru Kusano means "Fragrant" and "Field of Grass"

105
00:07:02,550 --> 00:07:04,150
which is represented for the fragrant field of sweet grass!

106
00:07:04,150 --> 00:07:05,950
Yuki Takeno means "Snow" and "Mountain Area"

107
00:07:05,950 --> 00:07:08,250
is for white snow covering the high mountain.

108
00:07:08,250 --> 00:07:10,650
Terumi Hoshino means "Beautifully glittering" and "Stars"

109
00:07:10,650 --> 00:07:11,950
is for the glittering stars in heaven.

110
00:07:11,950 --> 00:07:15,150
Yoko Okino means "Ocean" and "Offshore"

111
00:07:15,150 --> 00:07:17,350
is for the sparkling waves of the blue sea.

112
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:22,150
So, all four of them together are called "Earth Ladies".

113
00:07:22,150 --> 00:07:23,550
That's figures.

114
00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:27,850
Each of the names stands for a superb view of the earth.

115
00:07:27,850 --> 00:07:30,350
Yeah, but Earth Ladies broke up

116
00:07:30,350 --> 00:07:32,750
because of a quarrel between Terumi and Kaoru.

117
00:07:32,750 --> 00:07:35,750
So, only Yoko continued on as a singer.

118
00:07:36,750 --> 00:07:40,550
Anyway, I was surprised that Kaoru, the youngest of the four of us,

119
00:07:40,550 --> 00:07:42,550
turned out to be the first to get married.

120
00:07:42,550 --> 00:07:44,150
Actually, so did I.

121
00:07:44,150 --> 00:07:47,750
I thought Terumi would be the first to get married and settle down.

122
00:07:47,750 --> 00:07:51,250
Hey, I thought you once said something about your loved one?

123
00:07:51,250 --> 00:07:53,850
Yes, yes, tell us what happened to your relationship with the guy?

124
00:07:53,850 --> 00:07:55,150
Did you confess your love to him?

125
00:07:56,450 --> 00:07:59,150
Not really.

126
00:07:59,150 --> 00:08:03,250
Besides, like some people say, "Marriage is the tomb of love and trust."

127
00:08:03,250 --> 00:08:06,750
So, it's much easier to love him from a distance.

128
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:09,150
That way I can keep him in my heart as my ideal man.

129
00:08:09,150 --> 00:08:11,350
Hey, just what do you mean by that?

130
00:08:11,350 --> 00:08:13,050
Terumi...

131
00:08:15,450 --> 00:08:18,850
But who is that old man with the kid?

132
00:08:18,850 --> 00:08:19,850
Oh, yeah...

133
00:08:19,850 --> 00:08:22,150
Are you Kenzaki's brother or something?

134
00:08:22,150 --> 00:08:24,050
I'm...

135
00:08:24,050 --> 00:08:29,250
It's about time "Detective Samonji" will be starting.

136
00:08:29,250 --> 00:08:31,850
"Atsushi Maguma (23), Kaoru's manager" -Don't you want to watch it?

137
00:08:31,850 --> 00:08:33,450
I'll pass it up.

138
00:08:33,450 --> 00:08:35,350
In the meantime, I'm going to take a bath.

139
00:08:35,350 --> 00:08:36,950
Just tell me when it's over.

140
00:08:37,950 --> 00:08:40,950
But... As the food's getting cold,

141
00:08:40,950 --> 00:08:42,250
I'd like to have dinner together now.

142
00:08:42,250 --> 00:08:43,650
Please don't bug me.

143
00:08:43,650 --> 00:08:45,350
I said "Pass". Don't make me say the same thing over and over again.

144
00:08:45,350 --> 00:08:48,650
When will a loser like you get off telling me what to do?

145
00:08:50,150 --> 00:08:51,350
I'm sorry.

146
00:08:51,350 --> 00:08:53,250
Wait. Kaoru.

147
00:08:54,250 --> 00:08:56,450
She hasn't changed at all.

148
00:08:56,450 --> 00:08:59,350
She's always embarrassed to watch the programs she stars on,

149
00:08:59,350 --> 00:09:01,150
with other people.

150
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:03,850
Just as we planned.

151
00:09:03,850 --> 00:09:06,250
Are you really going to do it?

152
00:09:06,250 --> 00:09:09,550
Of course. That's why we invited you.

153
00:09:09,550 --> 00:09:11,350
Do what?

154
00:09:11,350 --> 00:09:13,750
We'll be waiting for you in the living room.

155
00:09:13,750 --> 00:09:14,850
Yoko, why don't you go first,

156
00:09:14,850 --> 00:09:16,450
and change into your costume in the restroom?

157
00:09:16,450 --> 00:09:17,450
All right.

158
00:09:26,950 --> 00:09:28,450
That's none other than

159
00:09:28,450 --> 00:09:31,850
the costume that the "Earth Ladies" wore at the time they debuted.

160
00:09:31,850 --> 00:09:35,850
I see. When Kaoru comes out of the bathroom...

161
00:09:35,850 --> 00:09:39,250
Yes. Three of us are going to celebrate her engagement

162
00:09:39,250 --> 00:09:41,850
