163
00:09:41,850 --> 00:09:46,350
It's so embarrassing to wear this costume, though.

164
00:09:46,350 --> 00:09:49,950
Great! It looks nice! Lovely Yoko!

165
00:09:49,950 --> 00:09:53,950
You're just too much! You know that?

166
00:09:55,950 --> 00:09:57,250
Thank you for waiting.

167
00:09:59,850 --> 00:10:02,650
Do you really want to do it?

168
00:10:02,650 --> 00:10:05,750
Well then, next I'll go get rejuvenated.

169
00:10:05,750 --> 00:10:08,850
Hey, Yuki. Hurry up. I also have to change into.

170
00:10:08,850 --> 00:10:09,850
See you later.

171
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:14,550
Hey, let's all write a few lines each

172
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:16,150
