173
00:10:17,950 --> 00:10:22,250
I wish you much love and happiness.

174
00:10:24,250 --> 00:10:25,450
Here you go.

175
00:10:25,450 --> 00:10:27,550
Okay then, next, Terumi.

176
00:10:27,550 --> 00:10:30,850
Don't mind me, I think I'll pass.

177
00:10:30,850 --> 00:10:33,250
It's a good opportunity to make peace with Kaoru.

178
00:10:35,650 --> 00:10:37,650
I guess I have no choice, then.

179
00:10:37,650 --> 00:10:39,550
Hey.

180
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:43,850
Did Kaoru really want to see Pops?

181
00:10:43,850 --> 00:10:50,150
Yeah, as she said, weirdo follows her around.

182
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:52,550
She wants him to find out who the man is...

183
00:10:53,750 --> 00:10:55,750
Once she moves in with me,

184
00:10:55,750 --> 00:10:58,550
