193
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:28,000
If Terumi dares to do that, then I can do this...

194
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:33,500
With a loving kiss.

195
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:37,100
Hey! Manager, why don't you write something to her?

196
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:39,000
No, I...

