00:11:49,300 --> 00:11:50,300
Please.

201
00:11:53,700 --> 00:11:57,500
"Congratulations"

202
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,200
I'm sorry,

203
00:12:01,200 --> 00:12:03,000
you don't have to if you really don't want to.

204
00:12:04,300 --> 00:12:06,500
No, I'm just glad.

205
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:10,800
Here, I changed clothes.

206
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:12,500
It fits you just right.

207
00:12:12,500 --> 00:12:15,100
Then, I'll go call Kaoru.

208
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:22,100
What's wrong with him?

209
00:12:22,100 --> 00:12:23,400
I have no idea.

210
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:33,000
Hey! None of you watched my drama seriously,

211
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:35,600
