214
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:41,700
Okay, well just wait for Kaoru to come.

215
00:12:44,100 --> 00:12:46,000
Where is she?

216
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:48,300
Well...

217
00:12:48,300 --> 00:12:51,300
