218
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:55,100
She may have become dizzy or fainted in the bathroom.

219
00:12:55,100 --> 00:12:59,100
Then, Mr. Kenzaki, you should go check it out.

220
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:03,400
