223
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:12,800
Don't tell me that...

224
00:13:14,100 --> 00:13:16,500
Kaoru! Now please come out from there.

225
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:18,800
Everyone is waiting for you.

226
00:13:18,800 --> 00:13:20,800
Mr. Kenzaki, open the door.

227
00:13:21,800 --> 00:13:23,000
Hurry!

228
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:25,000
Kaoru! I'm coming in!

229
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,000
Kaoru.

230
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:31,000
Kaoru.

231
00:13:32,000 --> 00:13:33,000
Kaoru!

232
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:41,460
Kaoru.

233
00:13:41,460 --> 00:13:42,760
What happened?

234
00:13:43,860 --> 00:13:45,060
How did this all come about?

235
00:13:45,060 --> 00:13:46,360
She still has a pulse.

236
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:48,360
We must get her to the hospital immediately. Her life depends on it.

237
00:13:49,460 --> 00:13:50,860
Hurry!

238
