239
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:01,360
Kaoru?

240
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:06,060
Hey! Kaoru! Are you all right?

241
00:14:06,060 --> 00:14:08,060
Kaoru!

242
00:14:08,060 --> 00:14:10,360
-Ran, call the ambulance! -Yes.

243
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:17,860
