244
00:14:17,860 --> 00:14:20,760
Room number 1 on the 28th floor.

245
00:14:22,560 --> 00:14:27,460
A 20-year-old living alone in this luxury condo.

246
00:14:27,460 --> 00:14:29,760
Some rich kid or something?

247
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:31,160
You don't know, Inspector?

248
00:14:31,160 --> 00:14:33,660
The Earth Ladies?

249
00:14:33,660 --> 00:14:36,360
Earth what? What's that?

250
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:37,360
Oh, yes.

251
00:14:37,360 --> 00:14:38,560
